item.title: Hello World
item.description: So I’m starting my blog again. I lost all my previous posts because I neglected the server my old blog was on. It needed maintenance, I couldn’t be bothered to fix it. Out with the old, in with the new. I think it’ll be easier to post this time round because I’ve set up a system that makes it really easy.
